1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,879
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:31,639
=Episode 5=
(In the dead of winter,)

3
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:35,930
(the evil god's smile
flared with a scorching warmth.)

4
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:43,140
Zhao.

5
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:01,220
Everyone.

6
00:01:02,260 --> 00:01:05,379
Zhao's flesh and blood
can cure this illness.

7
00:01:05,380 --> 00:01:06,059
I'll go first.

8
00:01:06,060 --> 00:01:07,939
- Don't push me!
- Don't push!

9
00:01:07,940 --> 00:01:10,660
- I'll go first!
- Don't fight! Stop it!

10
00:01:25,140 --> 00:01:26,300
No!

11
00:01:35,460 --> 00:01:38,020
(That woman in my dream
looks so much like me.)

12
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:41,060
(Could she be the wife
that Ye Zhao spoke of?)

13
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:44,660
(She's so cruel-hearted.)

14
00:01:44,820 --> 00:01:46,460
(If this dream is true,)

15
00:01:46,860 --> 00:01:48,820
(then Ye Zhao is quite pitiful.)

16
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:03,020
(Heavenly Dao has its rules.)

17
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:04,739
(Using immortal arts on mortals)

18
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:06,180
(will incur heavenly punishment.)

19
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:08,299
(At best, the flesh is flayed)

20
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:09,820
(and all power stripped away.)

21
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:11,180
(At worst,)

22
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:12,859
(the divine heart will shatter)

23
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:14,540
(and the soul will scatter.)

24
00:02:20,940 --> 00:02:23,060
(At that time, she was a demon.)

25
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:28,140
(At that time, she was a human.)

26
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:34,620
(That strange behavior)

27
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,900
(suggests a failed possession.)

28
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:38,900
(If this is true,)

29
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:40,540
(I have misunderstood her.)

30
00:02:41,220 --> 00:02:42,380
Baobao.

31
00:02:44,140 --> 00:02:45,219
Yes, Master?

32
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:46,819
Go to Ning Palace

33
00:02:46,820 --> 00:02:48,780
and investigate
their princess' background.

34
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:54,060
Then, get the herbs
according to these two prescriptions.

35
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:56,019
Remember.

36
00:02:56,020 --> 00:02:57,459
Do not use your power on mortals.

37
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:58,620
Alright.

38
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:12,140
So beautiful.

39
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:17,260
This seedling

40
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:19,539
(Helian Shu, Duke Rong)
hurts when pulled up.

41
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:20,980
But when caressed,

42
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:24,700
it feels intoxicating.

43
00:03:27,220 --> 00:03:29,259
That wretched Emperor
actually dared to send

44
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:30,980
Chu Xihe away right under my nose.

45
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:32,820
As long as she lives,

46
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:35,340
this kingdom will never belong to me.

47
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:37,780
Since Chu Xihe was locked up in prison,

48
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,300
we've been keeping watch.

49
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:42,140
We finally found our opportunity
on the day of Her Majesty's funeral.

50
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:47,979
What did you say

51
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:49,460
I am just now?

52
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:52,660
The Grim Reaper

53
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,540
with a heart of stone,

54
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,660
is vengeful to the core,

55
00:03:58,620 --> 00:04:00,259
and is capable of unspeakable cruelty.

56
00:04:00,260 --> 00:04:03,860
Please have mercy.

57
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:14,760
(Hall of State Affairs)

58
00:04:16,780 --> 00:04:19,140
Mother has never been defeated
on the battlefield.

59
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:20,820
How could this be?

60
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:22,540
How could this be?

61
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:35,540
Who are you people?

62
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:37,860
The ones who have come for your life.

63
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:02,419
Charge.

64
00:05:02,420 --> 00:05:03,580
Kill her.

65
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:25,700
A bunch of losers.

66
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,060
You're telling me there's no news?

67
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,900
You're courting death.

68
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:35,419
Your Grace,

69
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:37,380
we have caught
a strange, injured person.

70
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:39,419
Why haven't you brought them in, then?

71
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:39,979
Yes, Your Grace.

72
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:40,699
I'm sorry.

73
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:41,860
Bring him in.

74
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:55,819
Tonight's full moon.
There's a wild beast inside.

75
00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:57,019
(Baihua Hall)
We should leave.

76
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:59,020
With me here, you don't have to worry.

77
00:06:06,980 --> 00:06:09,019
Deep in the hills
where the hungry ghosts wail.

78
00:06:09,020 --> 00:06:10,859
Fear not, fear not,
for the cat will prevail.

79
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:12,699
Every full moon we'll gather and go.

80
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:14,699
To laugh and to sing
at the ghosts in the show.

81
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:16,340
I'll catch you all.

82
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:24,860
(Ye Zhao can smile too?)

83
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:31,020
(He actually looks quite good.)

84
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:33,860
Why did you two come here?

85
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:36,340
Bai said your wife has returned.

86
00:06:38,140 --> 00:06:39,300
She has returned.

87
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:43,060
But it feels like she hasn't.

88
00:06:47,700 --> 00:06:50,059
- My lady?
- My lady.

89
00:06:50,060 --> 00:06:51,500
We've missed you so much.

90
00:06:55,180 --> 00:06:58,300
Do we know each other?

91
00:07:01,060 --> 00:07:02,220
My lady,

92
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:05,820
why are you covered in scars?

93
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:08,740
You must be in pain.

94
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:14,739
It's just some bruises.

95
00:07:14,740 --> 00:07:16,300
There are no scars.

96
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:17,979
My lady,

97
00:07:17,980 --> 00:07:19,379
we've recovered.

98
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:21,060
The root-severing rite worked.

99
00:07:26,620 --> 00:07:28,060
Root-severing rite?

100
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:43,340
Where...

101
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:45,060
Where are they?

102
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:47,700
They're just lingering souls
of obsession.

103
00:07:48,380 --> 00:07:52,180
Now that their wish has been fulfilled,
they've gone to heaven.

104
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,700
Obsession?

105
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:56,179
You mean,

106
00:07:56,180 --> 00:07:57,820
they've passed away?

107
00:07:57,980 --> 00:07:59,460
It's been over 100 years.

108
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:02,660
Then,

109
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:06,940
what kind of wish did they fulfill?

110
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,020
Nothing really happened just now.

111
00:08:11,620 --> 00:08:13,060
To see you once more.

112
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:16,500
See me?

113
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,220
But

114
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:21,820
I've never seen them before.

115
00:08:22,060 --> 00:08:23,820
They don't recognize the appearance.

116
00:08:24,180 --> 00:08:25,620
They recognize the soul.

117
00:08:25,860 --> 00:08:27,140
After reincarnation,

118
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:28,460
the appearance changes.

119
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,260
But the soul

120
00:08:30,860 --> 00:08:32,140
never changes.

121
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:35,900
You mean

122
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:38,820
they waited here for over 100 years

123
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:41,700
just to see me?

124
00:08:46,860 --> 00:08:48,620
They just missed you so much.

125
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,939
You've contracted the Verdant Decay.

126
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:19,940
You can barely protect yourself,

127
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:22,739
and yet you dare to capture my people?

128
00:09:22,740 --> 00:09:23,939
I can't protect myself?

129
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:25,699
What do you mean by that?

130
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,060
In just a few days,

131
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:31,820
you will die from this vile plant
draining your blood and flesh.

132
00:09:38,180 --> 00:09:39,460
Are you trying to scare me?

133
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:44,379
Have you recently felt something

134
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:46,059
wandering through your veins?

135
00:09:46,060 --> 00:09:49,380
Have strange bruises been
appearing on your skin?

136
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:55,460
When the flower blooms,

137
00:09:55,820 --> 00:09:58,580
that will be the day of your death.

138
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:01,700
Leave, all of you.

139
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:12,580
Immortal, is there a cure for this?

140
00:10:25,140 --> 00:10:27,260
We must meet in person,

141
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:29,500
Your Grace.

142
00:10:40,810 --> 00:10:42,489
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

143
00:10:42,490 --> 00:10:45,369
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

144
00:10:45,370 --> 00:10:48,089
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

145
00:10:48,090 --> 00:10:49,729
♪Let the long shadows♪

146
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:55,330
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

147
00:10:55,370 --> 00:10:56,969
♪If in a dream♪

148
00:10:56,970 --> 00:10:59,729
♪I can hear your voice♪

149
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:02,569
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

150
00:11:02,570 --> 00:11:05,169
♪Let it be us♪

151
00:11:05,170 --> 00:11:09,969
♪drawing endlessly close♪

152
00:11:09,970 --> 00:11:11,729
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

153
00:11:11,730 --> 00:11:14,370
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

154
00:11:14,610 --> 00:11:17,329
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

155
00:11:17,330 --> 00:11:18,969
♪Not even in time♪

156
00:11:18,970 --> 00:11:24,649
♪to tell you how I feel♪

157
00:11:24,650 --> 00:11:26,169
♪If the rain won't stop♪

158
00:11:26,170 --> 00:11:28,929
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

159
00:11:28,930 --> 00:11:31,889
♪Let love go on♪

160
00:11:31,890 --> 00:11:34,449
♪Until forever♪

161
00:11:34,450 --> 00:11:39,089
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

162
00:11:39,090 --> 00:11:41,689
♪Until forever♪

163
00:11:41,690 --> 00:11:48,810
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
